I want to make the most addictive app EVER
text:
So, I was wondering... If dopamine can keep people addicted to an app, just how long can I keep them hooked? So I started researching dopamine, and I found that I need to include: -Constant positive re-enforcement -Fear of missing out -Anticipation for the future -Lots of notifications -Make them feel bad -Let them comment and like/dislike random things -Lots of bright colours

SO... Do you have any other ideas on how to make it addictive?
